product.name: Upgrade Club Car Precedent Golf Cart LED Head Light Kit, Golf Cart Headlight Kit with Bumper for Club Car Precedent Replacement or Upgrade for 2004-UP Golf Carts
product.description:
About ZOOMYIN
The company established the "ZOOMYIN" brand in 2020, mainly producing and selling golf cart accessories, such as golf cart LED light kits, vinyl seat covers, steering wheels and adapters, rear seat kits, rearview mirrors, chassis related parts, and other Plastic hardware accessories.
product.bullet_points:
• 【Reasons to Choose】 This one Golf Cart Headlight Kit use upgraded LED lights, more brighter and reduce energy consumption, no need to preheat to start when using, LED head lights last longer and extend your usage time.
• 【Lighting Effect】 Club Car Precedent Head Light effective lighting length is so far that your view will not be hindered whether you are driving at night on rough mountain roads or flat roads, it gives you a greater sense of security.
• 【Easy to Install】 The adaptive voltage to install this club car led headlight, lamp is 12V. If your output voltage is not 12V, you need to add a Voltage reduction unit, which is mainly used to update the original lamp.
• 【Package Included】 Club Car Headlight Includes headlight, short wiring harness, bumper (Note:doesn't include the harness of the golf cart itself; only the harness of the headlights)
• 【Our Services】 We committed to producing high quality and improved products with patented designs. If there is any problem with the product, please feel free to contact us and we will provide after-sales service for you as soon as possible.
